Class Rectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shapes

    public class Rectangle
extends RightAngle2DShapes
    Version:
    1.0

    This is a subclass of RightAngle2DShapes. This will create a Rectangle of a specified base and height.

    Author:
    Alex Wong wong4a@gmail.com

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Rectangle()
      Default method that will create a rectangle with a base of 2 and height of 1.
      Rectangle(double base, double height)
      This method will create a rectangle of a desired base and height that is specified.
